  "mission": "GiveDirectly is a nonprofit that lets donors send money directly to the world\u2019s poorest households. We believe people living in poverty deserve the dignity to choose for themselves how best to improve their lives \u2014 cash enables that choice.\n\nSince 2009, we\u2019ve delivered $700M+ in cash directly into the hands of over 1.5 million people living in poverty. We currently have operations in Bangladesh, DRC, Kenya, Liberia, Malawi, Mozambique, Morocco, Nigeria, Rwanda, Turkey, Uganda, USA, and Yemen.",
